Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:10.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...a person on this earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...who is more important to you than yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:19.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Does a person like that truly exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...something that seems like it should change my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:38.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please read this.\N- I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...giving a confession of love like the ones I've seen on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:46.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...wearing clothes I found in a magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...going on a date at a place everyone lines up to get into...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:54.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...kissing someone in a scene just like a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:03.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dead of night, I ask myself over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:08.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,..."it would have been good even if it wasn't me, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"It would have been good..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...even if it wasn't you, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"The guy next to me would've done just as well, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:22.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Was there any reason..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:25.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...it had to be the two of us in the first place?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:31.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It can begin at any time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and end at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:39.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that disposable...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that really love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't sold anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it doesn't have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:54.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling in love with someone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that some...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...incredible miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who threw a person away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,People aren't garbage, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this. I really hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the way the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...a person on this planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...who is more important to you than yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Does a person like that truly exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. This, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay. Stay safe.\N- Your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:51.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:05.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? How did it go yesterday with the girl I introduced you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:09.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Was a Doctor of Engineering a little too much for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She really has no luck with men, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:20.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was thinking that she isn't the kind of woman I would be able to get along with...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you just try going out with her once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Science lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I... class... just attendance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Science prep room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Science Preparation Room]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...you said you'd have the surgery if I let you touch my teeth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? That was so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:45.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was "teeth." Who says that, normally? "Can I touch your teeth?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I must've felt like they might make music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Music?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Teeth look sort of like the keys of a piano, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wonder, "which note would come from this person?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:04.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull back so far! This was when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...even now, sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...just every once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are times...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I think, "maybe music would come from this person."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I know no music will come out, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't touch people's teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing something like that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the lowest sort of thing you can do as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:41.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no way any musical notes will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...make sure of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is completely foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:25.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:34.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me a name... within 20 seconds of activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Give you...a name? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:39.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,5...seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- 4... 3...\N- No. Wait! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- 2... 1...\N- Q...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:45.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto\N(Q10)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is... Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Heita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the note "la."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been authenticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd met a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...who sounded the note "la."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:49.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Q10\N[Kyuuto]\NEpisode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:57.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,translation by sarujin\NQC by sayochama
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:05.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,GIRIGIRI FANSUBS\NNOT FOR SALE OR RENT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She looks like a human though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, she's a humanoid robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- A robot in the shape of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- So that means, it'll move?\N- If you flip the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put it back...before this gets any bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's flipped the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:40.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Close it! Hurry, close it!\N- What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:48.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh? You're being chased by a girl?\N- Close that! Close it! Close it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Who? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who?\N- I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Principal's Office]\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...what did you touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well... I just...\N- You touched something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You touched somewhere you can't say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...belong to Fukai Heita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, no, no...\N- Hey! What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:23.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Kyuuto is just saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kyuuto?\N- It's her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:30.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this countdown, and I freaked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:32.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of energy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:48.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of... I have no idea what kind of energy it runs on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not human strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...it is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:08.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Hey! Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It is indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:31.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What a gallant little thing, isn't it? Though I don't quite understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:34.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dutifully running along, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:44.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose... we've all seen something we shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should call the police after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:53.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The police, yes... We've learned too much of this secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:13:00.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If the owner is from some underworld organization... I wonder if they'd just let us go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Underworld organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A plug converter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So it runs on electricity...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We might get it working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:16.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we tell the police that I picked up a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you think they'd tell my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It probably wouldn't be just your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be in papers and things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Weekly magazines, talk shows, network news...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer do I have to stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:04.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nishimura-kun.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai-kun isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:18.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared with a girl and hasn't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down. Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:24.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay! Fukushima-san...\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miyazawa-kun.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Morinaga-kun.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yamamoto-san.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going to happen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Fujioka Makoto]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did that to my chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't a clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have seen the person's face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't...think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait! What? Wait! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:11.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto... is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot is a secret between the four of us, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's put it in the school and watch it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Does "4 of us" mean you're including me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided to put it in your class. You'll look after it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me? Why?\N- You've got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we take it to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:45.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We could... but then we'd have to tell the police that you'd touched a girl's molars...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that? Your parents will find out you're a pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so embarrassing. I'd bite my tongue and die first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And it wouldn't just be your parents... it'll be all over network news. You watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a learning-type robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:16.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it's just been born, so... Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach it lots, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:22.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do all this work? This has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:28.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who woke her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... shouldn't we just push the reset button?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be one, right? She's a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:39.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... All of us can just pretend we never saw anything. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:43.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've flipped the switch... there's no going back to the way things were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I only promised to look after you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...until classes are over for the day. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that alone. It's just someone's scribbles...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Scribbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. My time with you is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The city?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,City.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:03.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So look... Okay? That big one is the supermarket...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:06.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...then there's the steel tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:10.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's the shopping district with the greengrocer that a perverted old man runs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and over there is the coffee shop with the really good egg-salad sandwiches, London...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:16.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's also this really dingy zori shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... all of this is the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:24.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:25.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw, didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- You did, didn't you?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't tell anyone!\N- All I saw was a video of Kawai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:07.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying... Don't tell anyone that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with Kawai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm telling you not to tell anyone...\N- I see. You've been going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:16.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out with Kawai would completely destroy my image.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:20.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not... It's not like you can do anything threatening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no door...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why isn't there a front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Until you pay your rent, we have confiscated your front door. - The Management]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:42.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That greedy little landlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone calls for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:53.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A robot. She's a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The principal found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted to buy it... it'd take at least a hundred million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It can talk...and walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you change the light bulb?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:21.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this house... with a young lady here, the whole place gets brighter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:28.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:30.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:31.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:42.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I'm taking a bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me every little thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:53.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I saw the scar from Heita's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's really going to have it his whole life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:57.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita's pet fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:01.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:05.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked sort of dirty, so I cleaned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it turns out, I used boiling water...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:09.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Of course they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:12.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she bought new ones, so he wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:14.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... They look completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, weren't they striped?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:18.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely notice. I'm not responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:23.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Once they're mixed in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:25.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:30.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See! You can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:32.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hey! H-how was the h-hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:38.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:42.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:44.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they say you've gotten better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:46.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They said there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:54.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. But... How was the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I said... it was the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:05.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice the fish tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They look completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:18.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're dead anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:21.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not like they'll come back or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:24.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:27.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are cold-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:32.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Angelfishes' Grave]\NIf something bad happens to Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...what will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:38.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just think that these guys gave themselves in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:44.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone is to be punished for this, let it be me and not Heita.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:48.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me. It has to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:51.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Take-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.63,0:23:54.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Science Preparation Room]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than a place with no front door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:19.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's pretending nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make a fuss if no one else is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:40.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.64,0:24:44.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.18,0:24:49.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:52.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you have a reset button?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.19,0:24:54.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.86,0:24:57.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My left molars.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.66,0:24:58.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You do have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:08.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell something that important to someone so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.44,0:25:10.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:15.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.31,0:25:18.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:20.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! She blew the door off...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:22.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's cute, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.85,0:25:25.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Kawai-san. Do you see her as your rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:29.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:31.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.29,0:25:34.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking forward to learning with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:41.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Where should she sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.23,0:25:44.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next to Fukai-kun, of course. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:45.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She can have my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.97,0:25:48.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She talks funny too, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:51.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's weird, right?\N- Oh. No! It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.18,0:25:53.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's only just returned to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.18,0:25:54.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.65,0:25:56.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran into Fukai-kun, after not seeing him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.32,0:26:00.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By "a long time" I mean... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.09,0:26:03.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're actually... childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:04.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.36,0:26:05.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.49,0:26:07.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.33,0:26:09.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.33,0:26:11.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a huge coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.16,0:26:12.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Se... Sensei!\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.33,0:26:14.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.43,0:26:15.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Name? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.44,0:26:17.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.87,0:26:19.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.97,0:26:22.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.44,0:26:24.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.95,0:26:27.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Last name... Last name...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.16,0:26:44.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kyuuto Karen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.06,0:26:46.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Karen?\N- That's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.93,0:26:48.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He used the characters for "flower" and "love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:52.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. Now all of you introduce yourselves too. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.01,0:26:53.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.01,0:26:56.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki Reiji. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.51,0:26:57.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Souda Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.98,0:27:00.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.28,0:27:02.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotegawa Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.22,0:27:04.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.58,0:27:05.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Gojou Takuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.09,0:27:08.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Akagawa Shiori.\N- Kageyama Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.69,0:27:10.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miyazawa Saburou.\N- Okazaki Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.06,0:27:11.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimura Tomorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.76,0:27:16.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Guys, if you say your names that quickly Kyuuto-san won't be able to remember them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:18.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.60,0:27:20.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.51,0:27:28.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki Reiji, Souda Rika, Nakao Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.98,0:27:32.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kotegawa Yui, Fujioka Makoto, Gojou Takuya, Akagawa Shiori...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.51,0:27:34.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kageyama Satoshi, Miyazawa Saburou...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.51,0:27:36.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...Okazaki Asuka, Nishimura Tomorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.75,0:27:41.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.86,0:27:44.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What an overwhelming memory... She might be more amazing than Kawai.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.66,0:27:49.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that? Kawai-san's expression looked strained, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.63,0:27:51.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The head of the class may be facing a fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.83,0:27:54.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- If she falls, she'll just be another ugly girl, right?\N- Hey. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.14,0:28:00.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.71,0:28:06.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.48,0:28:09.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... standing out is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.48,0:28:12.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing out is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:16.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. At school, it's best to let things just flow by calmly, without standing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.36,0:28:19.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.79,0:28:21.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rule for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.19,0:28:22.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.00,0:28:27.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.60,0:28:29.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Try writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.74,0:28:33.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.57,0:28:36.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can write!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.54,0:28:38.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.04,0:28:39.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:43.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This...is the same as mine! You have to write the characters differently!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.38,0:28:45.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.52,0:28:50.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The characters are all the same, but... they're different for each person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.66,0:28:53.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The same... but different.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.63,0:28:56.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. So... try changing them when you write them this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.10,0:29:03.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.00,0:29:04.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.51,0:29:08.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.15,0:29:15.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you press...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.02,0:29:18.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the reset button?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.06,0:29:25.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not push it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.50,0:29:32.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo! Kubo, come here a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.17,0:29:35.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.20,0:29:36.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Write "Kyuuto Karen."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.74,0:29:39.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why don't you just ask a classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.17,0:29:41.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be bad to ask someone in my own grade, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:44.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.91,0:29:47.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just... look for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.65,0:29:48.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:50.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.12,0:29:52.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having the surgery again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.79,0:29:55.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a second-year again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.49,0:30:01.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.23,0:30:05.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Stay there! Keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.93,0:30:08.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Second-years are so carefree, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.03,0:30:11.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your class is all on edge from entrance exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.84,0:30:14.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kubo! Hurry up! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.64,0:30:18.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Dash! Hurry up! Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.08,0:30:22.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.48,0:30:26.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The world isn't fair, is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.92,0:30:27.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.95,0:30:31.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...they say humanity will be destroyed in the year 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.99,0:30:35.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It's not gonna get destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.03,0:30:37.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna ask for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.36,0:30:38.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask who?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.83,0:30:41.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be that rumor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.43,0:30:46.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that if you wrote down your wish and buried it under the steel tower it'd come true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.74,0:30:50.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's the destruction of humanity, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.58,0:30:52.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.01,0:30:54.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.88,0:30:58.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't even go to the tower to bury it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.52,0:31:05.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.23,0:31:09.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.90,0:31:12.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...you do not run with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.10,0:31:17.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot run with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.01,0:31:22.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is defective.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.71,0:31:29.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...they did repairs, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.48,0:31:32.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not perfect though.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.50,0:31:44.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.33,0:31:47.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will reset you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.00,0:31:52.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.77,0:31:56.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans don't have reset buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.51,0:31:58.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.51,0:32:03.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:06.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When humans wish to reset...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.19,0:32:09.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...what do they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.66,0:32:12.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.13,0:32:14.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.33,0:32:16.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fukushima.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.00,0:32:20.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's see... Miyazawa.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.13,0:32:21.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sensei.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.87,0:32:22.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:28.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you did not call Fujioka Makoto's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.44,0:32:31.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's right. He didn't.\N- Why'd you leave Fujioka out?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.04,0:32:32.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you call on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.28,0:32:34.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... there are certain circumstances, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.45,0:32:36.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What circumstances?\N- It's a little tough to...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.59,0:32:45.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What's going on? What did Fujioka do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.16,0:32:47.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't paid his tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.66,0:32:49.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of stuff at home, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.26,0:32:53.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why his name has been taken off the attendance roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.03,0:32:54.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:56.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.70,0:33:00.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a private school, right? And all of you are, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.21,0:33:04.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents are paying your high tuitions. Let's get back to class now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:07.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto. You sit down now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.05,0:33:09.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.75,0:33:11.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Wait. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.48,0:33:12.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.02,0:33:17.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to find Fujioka Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.79,0:33:19.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.19,0:33:23.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But Fujioka Makoto has not had his name called.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:27.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All humans have something that no one else can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.77,0:33:31.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard we try, we won't be able to understand, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.50,0:33:33.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's better to pretend we don't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.51,0:33:35.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's called "kindness."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.21,0:33:39.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will look for Fujioka Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.35,0:33:42.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I will have his name called.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.49,0:33:49.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.39,0:33:50.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:52.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.19,0:33:54.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.56,0:34:33.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... Just... Excuse me. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:05.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.97,0:35:08.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.00,0:35:10.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.67,0:35:15.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a secret, okay? A secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.88,0:35:18.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I found some bread flour, so we're making bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.51,0:35:20.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.51,0:35:24.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very therapeutic. You want to do it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.69,0:35:27.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.73,0:35:37.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of waking up, every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.83,0:35:40.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Things at my house are getting worse and worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.26,0:35:42.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I feel like I'll lose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.47,0:35:47.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd come to school and feel like I could hold on to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.91,0:35:50.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.51,0:35:54.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...school is the only place I can be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.28,0:35:56.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.88,0:36:00.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I think about what's to come, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.45,0:36:02.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling people that...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.45,0:36:05.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...would only cause them trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.19,0:36:08.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When people act differently out of consideration it makes me feel worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.26,0:36:13.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.56,0:36:15.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be okay to cause a little trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.60,0:36:17.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.57,0:36:20.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see everyone looking troubled...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.35,0:36:33.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.45,0:36:34.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.22,0:36:40.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.29,0:36:46.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been better if I'd never existed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.00,0:36:50.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.20,0:36:57.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans do not have a reset button.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.18,0:37:05.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why, when humans wish to redo something, they ask for help. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.25,0:37:10.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.82,0:37:14.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pull this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.46,0:37:15.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.39,0:37:17.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pull it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.60,0:37:19.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:21.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.43,0:37:23.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.80,0:37:26.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.77,0:37:30.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When you yell in a loud voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.01,0:37:33.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...someone will come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:37.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a rule among humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.45,0:37:40.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.29,0:37:48.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I made a mistake in what I have said?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.69,0:37:52.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if it were true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.87,0:37:58.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you scream at the top of your lungs, someone will come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.27,0:38:04.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If that really were a rule for people, that'd be nice, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.16,0:38:26.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.52,0:38:50.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.79,0:38:56.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.56,0:38:59.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.06,0:39:04.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.13,0:39:07.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.64,0:39:10.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.11,0:39:13.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.28,0:39:15.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.75,0:39:18.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.22,0:39:21.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?\N- It's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.62,0:39:25.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.29,0:39:28.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- They're asking for help, right?\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.26,0:39:29.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.79,0:39:31.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem super serious, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.93,0:39:34.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei. Do something for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.26,0:39:37.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an employee here. I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:40.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Back to our lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.14,0:39:43.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're so petty.\N- Don't call me petty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.31,0:39:47.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:50.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's get back to class now. Hurry up.\N- Please, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.75,0:39:52.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.55,0:39:57.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're asking for help, and we're just going to ignore them?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.29,0:39:58.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not cool, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.76,0:40:02.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Then, should we scream with them?\N- To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.29,0:40:03.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.70,0:40:05.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.96,0:40:08.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky? Like asking God for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.67,0:40:11.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know if gods exist. Why would we ask them?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.60,0:40:15.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If only a news helicopter or something were flying by... we'd scream then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.74,0:40:17.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.11,0:40:20.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one the first day it snowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.34,0:40:23.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! And a picture of our class was in the paper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.31,0:40:26.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- But it's not gonna snow...\N- We'd have to solve a crime or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.85,0:40:29.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That'd be impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.52,0:40:33.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,One might fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.53,0:40:36.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Today in Shibuya they're having a surprise concert, "Monolith."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.93,0:40:39.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.60,0:40:43.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say, "Monolith"? Those are rock bands!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.77,0:40:45.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All of Shibuya will be in a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.67,0:40:49.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's tell the newspaper about the concert and get that helicopter to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:51.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.24,0:40:57.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting excited about? We're in the middle of class!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.61,0:41:00.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.72,0:41:02.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.29,0:41:05.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not loud enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.82,0:41:10.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you yell louder, they'll never hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.95,0:41:37.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Go get your desks. Go on. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.05,0:41:38.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.59,0:41:41.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.33,0:41:47.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.40,0:41:53.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.20,0:41:56.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they're all going to say, "help" together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.91,0:42:00.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.42,0:42:06.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.89,0:42:11.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher and everyone in class knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.62,0:42:15.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But they all pretend not to notice, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.73,0:42:19.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that coldness...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.63,0:42:21.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...or kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.60,0:42:24.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably both.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.95,0:42:42.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.95,0:42:45.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They might not send up a helicopter just for a surprise concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.32,0:42:48.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we may have to take it down without a big climax, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.43,0:43:30.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.66,0:44:28.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Hot! Hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.30,0:44:33.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.57,0:45:52.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It really did fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.11,0:45:54.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.08,0:45:56.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.11,0:45:59.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must've told them about the concert today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.52,0:46:03.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst. I was really looking forward to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.32,0:46:04.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.67,0:46:25.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! You feelin' the love?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.89,0:46:37.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No one came to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.82,0:46:43.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No one came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.23,0:46:45.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.53,0:46:50.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.93,0:46:52.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.78,0:46:59.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.91,0:47:00.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.88,0:47:03.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.25,0:47:07.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Split it up! That's your share!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.00,0:47:22.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.27,0:47:23.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.34,0:47:27.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did today cracked me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.84,0:47:30.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And my hospitalization date's been finalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.81,0:47:33.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.34,0:47:34.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.25,0:47:37.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.31,0:47:40.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be causing trouble for everyone again...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.22,0:47:46.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.06,0:47:49.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...that night we thought about destroying the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.63,0:47:53.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.70,0:47:56.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought everything was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.80,0:47:59.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Having to go to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.24,0:48:04.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that because of that Mom and Dad got more and more exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.88,0:48:08.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That my sister's grades dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.95,0:48:10.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:13.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurt so much... I couldn't carry that responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.89,0:48:17.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A world like that... I thought it'd be better for it to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.12,0:48:22.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is it wasn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.13,0:48:25.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.83,0:48:28.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it isn't anyone's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.60,0:48:35.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.54,0:48:39.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Dingy zori shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.34,0:48:42.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stupid! Stupid! You're too loud!\N- Perverted old man's grocery...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.98,0:48:45.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bridge. Shopping district.\N- Quiet! Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.92,0:48:49.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes. That's right. Okay.\N- Cafe with delicious egg sandwiches, London.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.02,0:48:52.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Real estate agency's flag... flag... flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.69,0:48:55.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.93,0:48:57.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's right. It's our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.00,0:49:02.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. She's a little weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.70,0:49:10.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a gacha-gacha machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.41,0:49:13.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put money in a toy comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.01,0:49:15.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's never seen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.40,0:49:36.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want for humanity to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.77,0:49:41.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this city to keep going, even after I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.28,0:49:54.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think too, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.96,0:50:02.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.19,0:50:06.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.03,0:50:08.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.60,0:50:10.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.60,0:50:13.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.54,0:50:16.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.74,0:50:19.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here, but... it's gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.48,0:50:29.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't tell anything with this... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.42,0:50:34.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This part looks legible, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.56,0:50:40.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.83,0:50:44.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.47,0:50:52.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...world..."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.91,0:50:59.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The "world" has been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.89,0:51:13.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you call his name for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.60,0:51:16.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do anything irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.10,0:51:18.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a small person.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.60,0:51:21.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am a small man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.27,0:51:23.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.57,0:51:27.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fujioka-kun... How are you today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.21,0:51:30.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can say that if you want to, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.08,0:51:32.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.42,0:51:34.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd do...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.82,0:51:36.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've gotten old...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.52,0:51:40.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I never want to do anything that makes me think, "I wish I would have..."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.23,0:51:45.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not old at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.20,0:51:51.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.57,0:51:54.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I received it from Kubo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.24,0:52:01.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Man, he really doesn't miss a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.38,0:52:04.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.28,0:52:06.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.68,0:52:10.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you throw it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.02,0:52:13.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.02,0:52:14.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I know his number, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.89,0:52:18.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have the number in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.76,0:52:21.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.33,0:52:23.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.73,0:52:25.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper... paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.04,0:52:28.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The characters are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.84,0:52:33.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kubo-kun did not write it... it is not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.35,0:52:36.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.05,0:52:45.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.02,0:52:49.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that day, Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.36,0:52:52.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...hasn't spoken a single word.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.36,0:52:55.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kawai.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.00,0:52:56.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.27,0:52:58.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.07,0:53:00.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.44,0:53:01.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.51,0:53:04.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.24,0:53:07.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kotegawa.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.04,0:53:09.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that not being spoken to...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.78,0:53:11.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...was this painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.98,0:53:13.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigematsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.82,0:53:16.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.39,0:53:19.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.72,0:53:22.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.86,0:53:24.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.80,0:53:28.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Just now, I was just chatting, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.30,0:53:29.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Time for class...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.40,0:53:36.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.97,0:53:39.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't talk like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.44,0:53:45.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any saliva, so if you chew gum your teeth will stick together. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.09,0:53:52.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...world...]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.06,0:53:55.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.16,0:53:58.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave Kyuuto your cellphone number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.40,0:54:01.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.56,0:54:04.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... it seems she lost that paper, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.34,0:54:06.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...write it again for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.74,0:54:09.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why? You know it, right? Just tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.61,0:54:11.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.51,0:54:14.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wants the one you wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.01,0:54:16.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.11,0:54:18.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wants the one in your handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.92,0:54:24.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just write.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.12,0:54:27.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.26,0:54:31.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.64,0:54:48.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.65,0:54:51.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.45,0:54:54.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.08,0:54:56.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...just an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.05,0:55:00.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get too excited, you'll just be embarrassed later.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.19,0:55:04.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell him then, that second.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.19,0:55:06.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.26,0:55:07.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.33,0:55:12.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.77,0:55:15.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...my heart is filling with spite...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.54,0:55:18.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's kinda weird, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.58,0:55:21.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.21,0:55:24.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To try to keep him from seeing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.78,0:55:27.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I gritted my teeth and forced a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.62,0:55:31.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.96,0:55:34.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...deep inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.13,0:55:38.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I realized a switch had been flipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.80,0:55:44.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A switch I didn't know existed... one no one had told me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.40,0:55:46.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...had been flipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.94,0:55:50.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kaidan no katasumi ni...]\NIn a corner, on the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.31,0:55:52.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...suwari uzukumaru no ano hito ni...]\N...that person cowering, crouched...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.94,0:55:55.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...nani ga atta n darou]\N...I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.01,0:55:58.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai nani wo mitekita n darou]\NWhat did that person see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.35,0:56:00.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Hitogomi no naka de...]\NIn a crowd of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.32,0:56:03.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...niramiau danjou no aida ni...]\N...that man and woman glare at each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.15,0:56:05.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...nani ga okottarou]\N...I wonder what happened between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.29,0:56:12.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai donna jijou ga atta n darou]\NWhat circumstances led them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.80,0:56:21.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Itsuka boku wo yobidashita...]\NOnce, you called me outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.20,0:56:23.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...sensei ga donatteta sono scene ha...]\N...and the teacher yelled. That scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.94,0:56:25.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...donna dattarou]\N...I wonder what it looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.61,0:56:28.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai boku ha nani wo shitta n darou]\NWhat on earth did I learn from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.11,0:56:31.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Itsu kara ka tsuzuiteru...]\NOn the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.45,0:56:33.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...sensou no hate ni donna koto ga...]\N...of this war that's lasted since who knows when...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.98,0:56:35.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...matteru n darou]\N...I wonder what waits for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.92,0:56:43.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Soushite boku ni nani ga dekiru n darou]\NAnd what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.53,0:56:47.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Koto no shinsou ha nani mo...]\NThe truth of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.13,0:56:49.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...shitteiru you de shirienai...]\N...we feel like we know, but we can't learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.67,0:56:51.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Sore demo dou ni ka kou ni ka...]\NEven so, somehow or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.77,0:56:54.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...ikiteita naka ga nai]\N...It's like we were never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.87,0:56:57.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Muda ga atteba tarirarenai]\NIt's not enough to meet with futility...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.34,0:57:00.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Demo shinjirareru mono mo sukunai]\NBut there are too few things to believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.11,0:57:04.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tada hitotsu tashika na no ha boku no kimochi]\NThe only certain thing is my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.88,0:57:07.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kimi no sono koe wo kikashite yo]\NLet me hear that voice of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.78,0:57:10.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Shinjireru mono ga soko ni aru yo]\NThat's where I find something to believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.42,0:57:14.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tada hitotsu tashika na no ha omae to no toki]\NThe only certain thing is my time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.59,0:57:19.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kimi ga suki]\NI love you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.13,0:57:22.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.00,0:57:25.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you know to be true gets flipped upside-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.84,0:57:28.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,People can fall in love with whomever they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.24,0:57:31.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a place you can keep living?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.24,0:57:32.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.34,0:57:33.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.28,0:57:34.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...am in love.
